summary: Keppel Earl "Kep" Enderby QC  was an Australian politician and judge.
full_text: Keppel Earl "Kep" Enderby QC  was an Australian politician and judge. Enderby was a member of the House of Representatives, representing the Australian Labor Party between 1970 and 1975 and became a senior cabinet minister in the Gough Whitlam government. After politics, he was appointed a Justice of the Supreme Court of New South Wales.
title: Kep Enderby
